READYOS EDITOR HELPFEATURESF1 COPIES THE SELECTION OR CURRENT LINEF3 PASTES TEXT FROM THE CLIPBOARDF5 SAVES THE CURRENT FILECTRL+A SAVES WITH A NEW NAMEF6 TOGGLES SELECTION MODEF7 OPENS A SEQ OR PRG TEXT FILEF8 OPENS THE EDITOR HELP POPUPCTRL+N PAGES DOWNCTRL+P PAGES UPCTRL+E JUMPS TO THE END OF THE LINECTRL+F FINDS TEXTCTRL+G FINDS THE NEXT MATCHF2 AND F4 SWITCH APPSCTRL+B RETURNS TO THE LAUNCHERSELECTION USES ARROWS AND HOME TO MARK TEXTSELECTION IS LIMITED TO THE VISIBLE PAGESELECTION COPY KEEPS LINE BREAKS ON PASTELIMITSTHE EDITOR KEEPS UP TO 100 LINESEACH LINE CAN HOLD UP TO 79 CHARSLONGER LOADED LINES ARE CUT OFFTEXT AFTER LINE 100 IS NOT LOADED